column1: Uchi////Enjoyed the Mustang and Spicy Crunchy Tuna rolls
column3: and they didn't wow me. The Brussel Sprouts were my favorite. The Jar Jar Duck was great
column4: and unique. The Pho deconstruction was very unique
column5: but wasn't high on the flavor scale. The Foie Gras left us wanting more of the accouterments that came with the Foie. Fried milk was delicious.
